      <title>美国称在俄罗斯被拘留的士兵被指控“行为不当”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/us-says-soldier-detained-in-russia-accused-of-misconduct</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国陆军周一表示，一名美国士兵因“不当行为指控”在俄罗斯东部被拘留，这可能成为自入侵乌克兰以来两国关系已处于低谷的新的爆发点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/us-says-soldier-detained-in-russia-accused-of-misconduct</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 19:51:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
