    <item>
      <title>以色列称哈马斯停火提案未达到其要求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/israel-says-hamas-cease-fire-proposal-falls-short-of-its-demands</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列拒绝了哈马斯关于其已接受停火提议以结束加沙战斗的声明，并表示其部队将继续在拉法开展行动，以消灭巴勒斯坦激进组织。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/israel-says-hamas-cease-fire-proposal-falls-short-of-its-demands</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 19:20:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>沃伦敦促五角大楼对受制裁地区的星链使用采取行动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/warren-urges-pentagon-action-on-starlink-use-in-sanctioned-areas</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国参议员伊丽莎白·沃伦敦促国防部控制星链在俄罗斯和其他未经授权地区的使用，称 SpaceX 旗下的卫星业务对美国及其盟友构成“严重的国家安全威胁”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/warren-urges-pentagon-action-on-starlink-use-in-sanctioned-areas</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 19:04:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苏纳克称下次英国大选结果可能比民意调查显示的更接近</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/sunak-says-next-uk-election-may-be-closer-than-polls-suggest</link>
      <description><![CDATA[里希·苏纳克(Rishi Sunak)表示，下一次英国大选的结果可能比民调显示的结果更接近，这增加了出现悬浮议会、没有任何政党拥有全面控制权的可能性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/sunak-says-next-uk-election-may-be-closer-than-polls-suggest</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 18:46:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>习近平敦促马克龙帮助中国避免“新冷战”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/SD2NA9DWRGG000</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着欧盟日益与美国对安全风险和贸易紧张局势的担忧保持一致，中国国家主席习近平呼吁法国帮助抵御“新冷战”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/SD2NA9DWRGG000</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 17:33:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列拒绝哈马斯提出的加沙停火计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/hamas-says-accepts-proposal-for-cease-fire-with-israel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴勒斯坦激进组织哈马斯称，已同意加沙地带的停火提议，但以色列战争内阁一致拒绝了该提议，称其“远非以色列的必要要求”，粉碎了立即停火的希望。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/hamas-says-accepts-proposal-for-cease-fire-with-israel</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 16:59:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>前特朗普财务总监称科恩从个人账户中还款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/trump-found-in-contempt-a-second-time-in-hush-money-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名前特朗普组织财务官员告诉纽约一家法院，唐纳德·特朗普使用个人银行账户偿还了他欠一位前律师的大部分钱，该律师在 2016 年大选前收买了成人电影明星斯托米·丹尼尔斯的沉默。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/trump-found-in-contempt-a-second-time-in-hush-money-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 13:34:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>经过数周的动荡后，哥伦比亚大学取消了主要毕业典礼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/columbia-cancels-university-wide-commencement-ceremony</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于以色列与哈马斯战争引发的抗议活动扰乱了大学毕业季，哥伦比亚大学在校园内经历了数周的骚乱后，取消了原定于 5 月 15 日举行的主要毕业典礼活动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/columbia-cancels-university-wide-commencement-ceremony</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 13:09:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>更多风暴袭击休斯顿地区，数百人从洪水中获救</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-05-05/hundreds-rescued-from-texas-floods-as-forecast-calls-for-more-rain-and-rising-water</link>
      <description><![CDATA[休斯顿（美联社）——周一，休斯顿地区的洪水开始退去，居民们开始返回家园并评估损失，此前几天的强降雨袭击了该地区，并导致数百人获救——包括被困在屋顶上的人们。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-05-05/hundreds-rescued-from-texas-floods-as-forecast-calls-for-more-rain-and-rising-water</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 05 May 2024 04:20:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
